here as it is here

00:07:01.180 --> 00:07:03.190
as it is here, 10
to the 23rd out.

00:07:03.190 --> 00:07:04.960
But when the wave
function repeats,

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:06.260
it picks up this phase.

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:14.770
And that phase is a number
that lives in k-space, that

00:07:14.770 --> 00:07:15.898
lives in the inverse space.

00:07:15.898 --> 00:07:17.440
And that's why we
spent all that time

00:07:17.440 --> 00:07:21.790
