of interacting,

00:12:11.250 --> 00:12:14.190
where they're close enough
that there's some interaction.

00:12:14.190 --> 00:12:17.350
If there's no interaction,
and your atoms are really,

00:12:17.350 --> 00:12:23.270
really far apart,
then it's basically

00:12:23.270 --> 00:12:25.730
like you just have
isolated atoms,

00:12:25.730 --> 00:12:28.520
