00:55:39.547 --> 00:55:40.673
AUDIENCE: Excess electron.

00:55:40.673 --> 00:55:42.090
JEFFREY GROSSMAN:
Excess electron,

00:55:42.090 --> 00:55:44.400
but compared to silicon.

00:55:44.400 --> 00:55:51.360
Now, if I have an excess
electron sitting in my crystal,

00:55:51.360 --> 00:55:55.093
but really the crystal is
still kind of silicony,

00:55:55.093 --> 00:55:57.260
because I don't have many
of these excess electrons.

00:55:57.260 --> 00:55:59.720
