without thermal energy, right?

00:56:15.200 --> 00:56:17.990
I don't need to work
with my Fermi function,

00:56:17.990 --> 00:56:20.180
I did it chemically.

00:56:20.180 --> 00:56:23.750
I put an atom in there that
had a spare electron, right?

00:56:23.750 --> 00:56:26.030
And that is actually,
in fact, exactly what

00:56:26.030 --> 00:56:29.630
