00:56:32.670 --> 00:56:34.410
or an excess of electrons?

00:56:34.410 --> 00:56:35.490
AUDIENCE: N-type?

00:56:35.490 --> 00:56:37.690
JEFFREY GROSSMAN: N-type.

00:56:37.690 --> 00:56:39.272
