state of iron.

01:03:53.510 --> 01:03:55.940
And if you do it with
spin polarized on,

01:03:55.940 --> 01:03:57.920
then it allows those
up and down electrons

01:03:57.920 --> 01:04:00.140
to move relative to each other.

01:04:00.140 --> 01:04:07.065
